Revised SpeakEasy Color Palette Description
App Concept: SpeakEasy is a sophisticated, adult-focused language learning platform emphasizing authentic conversation and real-world communication. Unlike gamified competitors with cartoon mascots and bright green themes, SpeakEasy is refined and professional. Visual Identity from Icon:
Rich Black/Charcoal (#001300) — The dominant color, conveying elegance, sophistication, and premium quality
Warm Gold/Honey (#ECD069) — Primary accent suggesting achievement, warmth, and encouragement
Sunset Orange/Coral (#ED8E52) — Energetic accent for calls-to-action and highlights
Ocean Blue (#2282BE) — Trustworthy, calm secondary accent for informational elements
Soft Cream (#F9F9DD) — Warm, inviting backgrounds
Mood & Differentiators:
Premium & Elegant — Black and gold evoke luxury, like a high-end language school
Warm & Human — Sunset and golden tones feel personal, not sterile or robotic
Confident & Trustworthy — Blue accents add reliability without dominating
Adult & Refined — No neon, no cartoons, no gamification aesthetic
Avoid: Bright lime green (Duolingo), neon colors, childish palettes, overly playful vibes